#define WrestleWin ["That's it?! You wasted my time with that?! You're not even worth a comic book cover!","Stop complaining! I barely touched you! Everything on this world is so cheap and fragile!","I'm supposed to be the hero here! Why are you making me waste my time on bugs like you?!","Look at you, broken on the floor. On Earth-Prime, people knew when to stay out of the way!","You're ruined! Completely ruined! Don't you dare look at me like I'm the bad guy!","You thought those pathetic little powers would stop me?! I'm SUPERBOY! I'm the real deal!","I'll kill you! I'll kill you to death! Stop making me look like the villain!","You're all just fake! Cheap, grim, modern imitations! My world was better than yours!","See?! You couldn't even bruise my suit! You don't belong in the same multiverse as me!","Get up and apologize! You're ruining everything! You're ruining MY universe!","You hit me! WHY DID YOU HIT ME?! I'm trying to SAVE reality!","You were supposed to be a hero! But you're useless! All of you are useless!","I had a life! I had a girlfriend! I had a family! And you made me destroy you!","You forced my hand! You see what you made me do?! This is ALL YOUR FAULT!","Stay down! On Earth-Prime, the good guys always won, and I'm the ONLY ONE LEFT!","I'M NOT CRAZY! I'M NOT BAD! YOU'RE THE ONES WHO CORRUPTED EVERYTHING!","You almost ripped my armor! DO YOU KNOW HOW HARD THIS IS TO REPAIR?!","I just wanted to go home! Why couldn't you just let me go home?!","I smashed your shield! I smashed your team! I'll smash this whole world if I have to!","Look at what you made me do to you! You ruined your own world, not me!","I AM SUPERMAN! I'M THE REAL SUPERMAN! SAY IT! SAY IT BEFORE I HEAT-VISION YOUR FACE OFF!","You thought you were stronger than me?! NO ONE IS STRONGER THAN SUPERBOY-PRIME!","I tore right through your energy! I tore right through your team! NOTHING CAN STOP ME!","You're supposed to be a legend, but you're just another corpse lying in my way!","I'll punch reality until it fixes itself! I'll punch it until everything goes back to the way it WAS!","You hold the power of a cosmic god, AND YOU STILL LOST TO A TEENAGER FROM MAINE!","I don't care about your cosmic balance! I don't care about your timeline! I JUST WANT MY EARTH BACK!","I shattered the walls of the Bleed just to put my fist through your chest! HOW DOES THAT FEEL?!","You thought you were a fundamental law of existence? I'M SUPERBOY-PRIME! I WRITE THE LAWS!","Look at you... bleeding star-matter. You're just as fake and pathetic as all the rest of them!","I RETCONNED YOU! DO YOU HEAR ME?! I PUNCHED TIME SO HARD YOU NEVER EVEN EXISTED!","YOU CREATED THE MULTIVERSE AND IT STILL WASN'T GOOD ENOUGH! SO I BROKE IT!","THERE IS NO CRISIS I CAN'T SURVIVE! THERE IS NO GOD I CAN'T KILL! I AM THE REAL HERO!","(Screaming hysterically into the cosmic void) I WON! I WON AGAIN! WHY ISN'T EVERYTHING BACK TO NORMAL YET?!","You controlled all of space and time... but you couldn't control ME! EVERY PRETTY LITTLE UNIVERSE BELONGS TO SUPERBOY-PRIME!!!" ]

#define WrestleDefeat ["No! Cheat! You cheated! You used red sun light! THAT'S NOT FAIR!","Let me go! My suit... my armor... you ruined it! I'm calling my parents!","Stop looking at me like that! I'm the good guy! YOU'RE THE BAD GUY HERE!","I'm losing my strength... No, no, NO! I'm Superboy! I'M SUPERBOY-PRIME!","When I get my powers back, I'm going to punch your entire planet into dust!","Magic?! That's so stupid! Magic shouldn't even work against real Kryptonians!","You didn't win! My solar cells just drained! It doesn't count!","This world is so terrible! Nothing works the way it's supposed to on Earth-Prime!","Get off me! You're breaking my suit! Do you know how hard this was to build?!","I hate you! I hate this timeline! I hate ALL OF YOU!","Why won't you just let me have my world back?! What did I ever do to you?!","You think you're heroes?! Real heroes don't gang up on a kid!","My head hurts... my vision is going dark... You're all monsters!","I was supposed to have a normal life! I had a prom! I had a girlfriend! AND YOU TOOK IT ALL!","You didn't beat me! I just... I just need more sunlight! That's all!","OW! That hurt! YOU'RE NOT ALLOWED TO HURT ME!","My armor is leaking solar energy... No, no, stay inside! STAY INSIDE ME!","I'm bleeding... Kryptonians don't bleed under a yellow sun! WHAT DID YOU DO TO ME?!","I'll kill you... I swear I'll kill you... Just... stop hitting me...","Why is everyone so mean to me?! I just wanted everything to be GOOD again!","NO! Not the Speed Force! Don't put me back in the dark! IT'S TOO COLD IN THERE!","I'M SUPERMAN! YOU CAN'T IMPRISON SUPERMAN! IT'S NOT RIGHT!","I gave up everything for this multiverse! And this is how you repay me?!","My suit is completely shattered... my power is fading... Why does nobody love me?!","(Screaming uncontrollably) I HATE THIS UNIVERSE! I WANT TO GO HOME! I WANT MY EARTH BACK!","You stole my solar energy... I feel so small... I feel so weak...","I fought through the Bleed... I threw planets... How are you still standing?!","I'm not a villain... I'm just Superboy... Why won't anyone believe me...?","The sun... it's so far away... Everything is getting dark...","You broke my fists... I can't punch time anymore... I can't fix anything...","You're unmaking time... but if you destroy this reality... where do I go...?","I punched history until my knuckles bled... and it still wasn't enough to save Earth-Prime...","I wielded the power to rewrite creation... and I'm still just a lonely boy in the void...","No... don't erase me... If I die here... nobody will remember the real Superboy...","(Quiet, broken weeping) It's all gone... Laurie... my mom... my dad... I'm so sorry..."]

